    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "I just took a closer look, and you are right -- v1.4.0 did log to stderr, even though there was [code](https://github.com/flashbots/mev-boost/blob/v1.4.0/cli/main.go#L74) to set it to stdout. But this code set it for logrus in general but not the specific instance!\r\n\r\nThis change in log output to stdout was introduced in https://github.com/flashbots/mev-boost/pull/401 - released in v1.5.0\r\n\r\nThe intention was to already log to stdout before, and this PR was meant to fix it.",
